items.name: home
items.html:
Sample page

Hero
Cards
Form
Admin

This is a sample landing page

This hero section have been built using the integrated block editor.
Each section of this page can be edited and customized with ease using the integrated style editor or also usingTailwindCSSas it has been integrated natively into the block editor.

The block editor has also been enabled with autosave (every 5 seconds)!
No need to remember to click the save button!

Take me to the Admin panel

Simple components

Can be easily composed to create custom, arbitrarily complex and personalized components.

You can also

Add custom stylesheets or even scripts, check the console to se a secret message 😉

Forms and other elements

All forms and other elements are supported too.
With the power of JS you can also freely customize them to fit your needs, load custom pages, interact with API and more!

This is the most secret section of this home page

 Let us know if you've discovered the secret code in the console by entering it in the form below!
